{"tid":1954981,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"摩笛來了，走呀","createTime":"2020-04-02T07:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T12:15:26.000Z","uid":93519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"df076e0a9fc6813481d9e3ed5586c2d2cbe9ad88","tid":1954981,"uid":93519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2425210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2425210&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=d9d3e2e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2425210</a><br />\n<br />\n走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利列出20隻亞太首選股票，包括阿里巴巴(09988)、友邦保險(01299)等。<br />\n<br />\n大摩發表報告指出，MSCI日本以外亞太指數成分股公司中，擁有堅實資產負債表且收益狀況，相對比較明確的行業領頭羊未來6至12個月可能會有出色表現。<br />\n<br />\n除友邦保險和阿里巴巴之外，報告亦列出騰訊控股(00700)、新鴻基地產(00016)、海螺水泥(00914)、中國移動(00941)、招金礦業(01818)等。<br />\n<br />\n大摩第二大建議增持的目標是澳洲股票；又看好訊息技術、通訊服務和材料類股。<br />\n<br />\n根據摩根士丹利的內部分析模型，所列20隻股票中，13隻在盈利能力和增長潛力方面得分最高"},{"pid":"a9738a45c15a4d6b2a499b40473593f112d5ed0f","tid":1954981,"uid":181649,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"大摩吹雞 無得留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078db21e324e9c4bd81b2dc151a83cfda5ef832e","tid":1954981,"uid":89538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"正 無揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bd62bce841927bb0e0849f8fdbb2cff662661f","tid":1954981,"uid":44562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"準備撈 914 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1307d61ec1ae87f2915b9be1625bc3a889d24f","tid":1954981,"uid":52022,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:33:48.000Z","msg"